    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior presents very well, though it does show minor signs of road wear such as light stone chips on the hood and small surface scratches on the rear bumper. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as they should. It offers a reliable driving experience and is ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
